Meta description tags are an important aspect of on-page SEO (Search Engine Optimization).
They provide a brief summary of the content on a web page and appear in search engine results pages (SERPs)

They should provide a brief and accurate summary of the content on the page.

Include relevant keywords in the meta description, especially those that users are likely to search for.

<meta name="description" content="Explore a wide range of houses for sale in Kathmandu with our platform. 
Find your dream home in Nepal's vibrant capital city. Discover affordable and luxury properties, backed by expert guidance.
Start your journey to homeownership today.">
